  "text": "To process texts efficiently and fast, domain patterns are ideally implemented as finite state automata (FSAs), a methodology pioneered in the FASTUS IE system [CITATION_1] . Although this paradigm is simple and elegant, it has the disadvantage that it is not easily portable from one domain of interest to the next.",
